def filtered_data(column):
    q1 = column.quantile(0.25)                 
    q3 = column.quantile(0.75)
    iqr = q3 - q1
    filtered = (column >= (q1 - 1.5 * iqr)) & (column <= (q3 + 1.5 * iqr))
    return filtered
